Using only common, neutral, everyday language, create ${n} short, natural sentences in ${targetLanguage} using these words: ${words}.
Each sentence should use one target word once, in a typical, high-frequency structure suitable for learners.
Return only ${targetLanguage} sentences.
Enclose the translated target word in < >.
Return a JSON dictionary exactly in this format (no header, no extra text):

{
  "sentences": {
    "original_word1": "sentence in ${targetLanguage} with <translated_word>",
    ...
  }
}